Introduction

Yao Mingming , also known as Yao Bonan , is a singer under One Cool Jacso Entertainment. He is a former member of the groups UNINE and BLK. He debuted on October 23, 2020, with the single "Mirror Me". Mingming was a pre-debut member of SEVENTEEN and appeared on the reality show Seventeen TV. At some point in 2013 he left the group and agency.In 2017, Mingming joined the survival show MIXNINE. He ranked 10th in the finale, and hence did not make it into the winning lineup. He was confirmed to be a new member of BLK in April 2018, but never made his official debut with them as they disbanded a few months later. In 2019, he participated in the Chinese survival show Youth With You. He ranked third place, making him a member of the project group UNINE.
